text:
That's the high school where we're
going to have the live this time.
It's a splendid school building... indeed.

Going to other schools feels a bit
nerve-wracking, doesn't it?

Oh, I get it.
You start looking around nervously.

Is that how it is for you too,
Choco-senpai and Juri-chan...!?

I'm nervous too!
There are lots of older brothers and sisters there, so...

Hehe, that's right.
Everyone's older than Kaho, after all.

But it'll be okay!
With everyone there, it's bound to be really fun!

I see, thank you.
Let's do our best together, Kaho!
